    sender_email = os.getenv("EMAIL_ADDRESS")
    sender_pass = os.getenv("EMAIL_PASSWORD")
    smtp_server = os.getenv("SMTP_SERVER", "smtp.gmail.com")

    msg["From"] = sender_email
    msg["To"] = recipient
    msg["Subject"] = subject
    msg.attach(MIMEText(body, "plain"))
